(3, 3, 0, 0, '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt -14.2pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">T&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">The Acceptance Test Run OR the performance test\r\nwill be held after commissioning by the OEMs representative engineers in the\r\npresence of customer engineers or a third party as in agreement in the contract\r\nguarantee clause. The equipment’s capability of delivering the output as\r\ndesigned and guaranteed is proved by conductance of the tests. Prior approval\r\non the method and procedures are obtained from client or client’s authorized\r\nrepresentative by the supplier. This is purely to prove the guarantee of the\r\ncontract.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt -14.2pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.05pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">A performance test is usually carried out after the\r\nconstruction or retrofit of a plant. It verifies its guaranteed parameters and\r\nfunction as intended. It is also carried out to check the present operating\r\nparameters and to find out lacunas in operation.</span><a name=\"_GoBack\"></a><b><u><span style=\"font-size:24.0pt;\r\nfont-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><br>\r\n<!--[if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--><br>\r\n<!--[endif]--></span></u></b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 0.05pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">A performance test can help maximize plant\r\nefficiency, reduce plant emissions, and minimise operating costs by identifying\r\nany shortfalls in the efficiency and capacity of the plant and providing\r\nrecommendations for recovery and performance improvement.<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-left: 0.05pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Equipment and plant performance tests may be carried out for different\r\npurposes and are related to machine history, maintenance schedules and running\r\ntime, i.e.:<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Preliminary performance tests on plants during the start-up stage<o:p></o:p></span></li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Performance diagnostics&nbsp;before and after maintenance&nbsp;services<o:p></o:p></span></li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Contract&nbsp;acceptance and compliance&nbsp;testing<o:p></o:p></span></li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Tests on machinery and plants for monitoring performance and\r\nestablishing corrective action to enhance performance<o:p></o:p></span></li><li style=\"margin-left: 0.25in; line-height: 12pt; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:\r\n&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:\r\nEN-IN\">Performance tests in normal operating conditions for&nbsp;production\r\nplanning&nbsp;and&nbsp;cost optimization&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>', '', 1571079332, 2, -1),
(4, 4, 0, 0, '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Industrial and Thermal Power Plants are the\r\nbackbone of any industry. The main aim is uninterrupted Power / Steam\r\ngeneration with minimum auxiliary power consumption. <o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">In the present scenario, energy conservation &amp;\r\nenergy security are the serious concern for all industries. To enrich the\r\nsustainable development, the industries has to take energy efficiency measures\r\nin this arms for reducing energy bills, increase profit by competitiveness,\r\nReduce energy imports and conservation of limited sources.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21.3pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 21.3pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Various power consuming equipment installed for the\r\npurpose of meeting the outcome of the installation may or may not function\r\nindividually or in total and may consume power more or less as predicted by the\r\ndesigners and suppliers of the equipment. This phenomenon is achieved by\r\nrunning the equipment at their full / partial loads at the case may be and the\r\nenergy consumption of individual as well total equipment is recorded. Various\r\naspects of improvements are suggested to meet the target in line with the\r\ndesign as well state of art improvements by carrying out energy audit at some\r\nfrequencies and to achieve optimum operating cost. Expertise man power along\r\nwith adequate instruments with calibration are utilized during the audit and\r\nthe audit findings are reported for efficient running of the plant. With the\r\nexpertise available with us, our company can readily take up such studies and\r\nhelp our clients in reduction of power consumption as well increase power /\r\nsteam generation.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify;text-indent:18.75pt\"><b><u><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;\">Why\r\nSPEL for Energy Audit:<o:p></o:p></span></u></b></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin: 0in 0in 0.0001pt 18.75pt; line-height: normal; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">SPEL’s Special offer is a Walk through audit,\r\ntargeted audit detailed energy audit based on the need of client in Process\r\nPlant, Co-generation, Captive and Utility power plants. We track during energy\r\naudit by verifying, monitoring and analysing the use of energy which includes\r\nsubmission of Technical report containing recommendation for improving\r\nEfficiency with cost benefit analysis and action plans to reduce energy\r\nconsumption.<o:p></o:p></span></p><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style