(5, 5, 0, 0, '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">When there is a need for improvement as\r\nwell trouble free operation, based on the history of operation, failure\r\nhistory, inadequate performance of individual equipment or to improve the installed\r\ncapacity of the plant equipment, many times dismantling of equipment and\r\nfurther assembling back, or some time retrofitting major modified equipment are\r\nnecessary. Expertise man power, tools and tackles, with prior experience of\r\nerection are the requirement. Such services are often requested by many clients\r\nfor which we can readily take up the service jobs of power plants.</span></p>', '', 1571080754, 2, -1),
(6, 6, 2, 0, '', '', '<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\">Many utilities and Industries, owing to\r\ntheir preoccupation, continue to run their plant and equipment with deficiency\r\nin operation, frequent failures, varied operating procedures which resulted in\r\noperational losses, decreased profit, stress to the management as well the\r\noperators. Such type of operational issues, failures and difficulty in\r\nsustained operation of the equipment call for specialized experts’ study on the\r\nplant. Vast experienced experts available with us can study the issues and\r\nsuggest improvements to avoid operational losses on frequent failures, tripping\r\nof equipment and so on.</span></p>', '', 1571080800, 2, -1),
