(18, 2, 0, 0, '', '', '<span style=\"font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;, serif;\">Pre Commissioning, also referred as\r\nstatic commissioning, starts when a system or subsystem achieves Mechanical\r\nCompletion. The safety monitoring activities will change at this transition as\r\nfluids (water, air, nitrogen, hydrocarbons, etc.) are introduced into sections\r\nof the facility to support testing, cleaning, flushing, and other pre-commissioning activities. Attached is a typical list of Pre-Commissioning\r\nItems:</span>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n<ul><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">1.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Temporary\r\nScreens, Strainers and Blinds – Doing walk down checks, witnessing</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">2.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Air and\r\nSteam Blowing – Cleaning the systems</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">3.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Flushing,\r\nChemical and Mechanical Cleaning</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">4.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Cleaning\r\nand Passivation – Ensure 100% cleaning to ensure protection.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">5.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Electrical\r\nSystem Energizing – Essential pre commissioning of equipment</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">6.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Instrumentation\r\nVerification – A must for total system readiness for commissioning.</span></li><li style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: -0.25in;\"><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">7.<span style=\"font-variant-numeric: normal; font-variant-east-asian: normal; font-stretch: normal; font-size: 7pt; line-height: normal; font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\r\n</span></span><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Checking\r\nof all logics and controls of all systems.</span></li></ul>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;mso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">Commissioning:</span></b></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"margin-bottom:0in;margin-bottom:.0001pt;text-align:\r\njustify;line-height:normal\"><b><span style=\"font-size:7.0pt;mso-bidi-font-size:11.0pt;font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;\r\nmso-fareast-font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;;mso-fareast-language:EN-IN\">&nbsp;</span></b></p