uipment descriptions and operating principles\r\nfor the major equipment types. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:5.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Discuss the key maintenance components of that equipment. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:5.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Highlight important safety issues. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:5.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Point out cost and energy efficiency issues. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:5.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Highlight any water-related efficiency impacts issues. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-top:0in;margin-right:0in;margin-bottom:5.5pt;\r\nmargin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Provide recommended general O&M activities in the form of\r\nchecklists. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\" style=\"margin-left:0in;text-indent:0in;mso-list:l0 level1 lfo1\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;\r\ncolor:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Where possible, provide case studies. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;mso-fareast-font-family:\" goudy=\"\" oldstyle=\"\" std\";=\"\" color:#221e1f\"=\"\" lang=\"EN-US\"><span style=\"mso-list:Ignore\">•<span style=\"font:7.0pt \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\"\"=\"\">                     \r\n</span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;color:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Ensure trouble free operation with optimum output as decided by\r\nclients. <br></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"Default\"><span style=\"font-size:11.0pt;color:#221E1F\" lang=\"EN-US\">Above\r\nconsiderations are the main objectives of O&M services, and with aiming at\r\nthese objectives, our company takes up O&M services and serve customers\r\nwith expertise man power, added with technical knowledge in the fields of\r\nOperation and Maintenance of the equipment. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></p>\r\n\r\n', '', 1566411209, 2, -1);
